Too Expensive;

If this game was 30 USD I'd accept the huge costs on DLC. But it's not. And it's going to be a damn shame when this game is dead because of it. Left 4 Dead 2 has a larger monthly playerbase than this over priced moneygrab.  If you're considering buying this wait until it goes on sale in 2016 for 5 ♥♥♥♥in dollars like Titanfall did.

